{"tid":1070722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"暗戀咗一個人好耐","createTime":"2019-03-21T01:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T01:24:18.000Z","uid":153670,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23f81d11435b3ecc782b0bbeb480a63159226e42","tid":1070722,"uid":153670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:03:33.000Z","msg":"由暗戀你，到放棄你。我終於因為畢咗業，時間的沖洗，令到我慢慢忘記你，唔再因為你影響到自己嘅心情。<br />\n但係點解你要在我正正打算重新出發嘅時候你黎搵我，點解要重新比希望我。點解你要主動搵我，再慢慢消失，呢種由天堂落地獄嘅感覺，真係好難受。點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奉勸如果對一個人無興趣，請你唔好搵佢。因為真係好容易令人誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3d3cfe4781600d2eb41668c928118299d131f8","tid":1070722,"uid":155628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:05:18.000Z","msg":"點解要暗戀？ 唔識去溝佢？"},{"pid":"1ce80065989edddfc193d71034bcd059e907547f","tid":1070722,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:11:28.000Z","msg":"不要去暗戀去強姦"},{"pid":"d53b63e6c0bb2ff82cdae23f45bdd6f730915464","tid":1070722,"uid":210297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"搵你傾兩句就以為有機，唔好咁癲啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4599493e377408a8bbd3f1f93a68b04f617bc54","tid":1070722,"uid":153670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e3d3cfe4781600d2eb41668c928118299d131f8","tid":1070722,"uid":155628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:05:18.000Z","msg":"點解要暗戀？ 唔識去溝佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:20:10.000Z","msg":"因為人地之前有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a399f217fcb0db4dac4979d072d42bd3e4602b20","tid":1070722,"uid":153670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d53b63e6c0bb2ff82cdae23f45bdd6f730915464","tid":1070722,"uid":210297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"搵你傾兩句就以為有機，唔